WEBVTT

00:07:29.332 --> 00:07:32.317
These investments 
offer significant benefits

00:07:32.317 --> 00:07:34.518
beyond just being ready for the epidemic.

00:07:34.518 --> 00:07:36.982
The primary healthcare, the R&amp;D,

00:07:36.982 --> 00:07:39.812
those things would reduce 
global health equity

00:07:39.812 --> 00:07:43.502
and make the world more just 
as well as more safe.

00:07:43.502 --> 00:07:46.864
So I think this should absolutely
be a priority.

00:07:47.514 --> 00:07:48.980
There's no need to panic.

00:07:48.980 --> 00:07:53.469
We don't have to hoard cans of spaghetti
or go down into the basement.

00:07:53.469 --> 00:07:57.309
But we need to get going,
because time is not on our side.

00:07:57.309 --> 00:08:03.524
In fact, if there's one positive thing
that can come out of the Ebola epidemic,